snippet.title: Fallen Angel [PC] Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Fallen Angel is a 2D pixel art, hack and slash RPG where you take the role of Lucifer in a quest to regain paradise.

Support the kickstarter campaign: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fallenangel/fallen-angel-a-pixel-art-hack-and-slash-rpg

Fallen Angel will be available for PC (Steam) in June 2020, with Switch, Xbox One, and PS4 versions being considered.
